# Frontend environment (optional)
#
# Local development (default): do NOT set VITE_API_BASE_URL.
# The app calls same-origin `/api/v1`; Vite proxies `/api` -> `http://localhost:3000` (see vite.config.ts).
#
# Use an override only when the SPA truly talks to another origin (e.g. staging):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.example.com/api/v1
#
# Avoid in dev — causes CORS and wrong paths:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
